Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.11,0:00:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.55,0:00:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.59,0:00:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧地 抱住我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.59,0:00:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什么表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 刚才真是对不起 说得稍微过火了点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.27,0:00:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放在心上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没情调
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:01:02.21,Logo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2400,0)}{\move(620,200,660,200,,)}{\fscx200\fscy200}灵风工作室
