Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:08.42,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\pos(350,400)}翻译\N\NSAWA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:08.42,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\pos(680,400)}校对\N\N小秘
